channel.title: Cabbage
channel.description:
Why does Andrew Gower like cabbage so much?
If you put Andrew in your notes it renames it to "Cabbage.", and before he closed his clan chat his title was "Cabbage.". He also made a post on RS forums where he mentioned cabbage like 999999999999999999999 times :confused: :confused:
Hi Newty real topic real question
